{"about_the_game":"<strong>Warning:</strong> This is a <strong>DEMO</strong> version of the final game. We are <strong>4 recently graduated Portuguese Game Developers</strong> <u>trying to start a Game Studio</u>.<br><strong>Every donation is appreciated</strong> and will contribute to the <strong>development of new games</strong> and to <strong>improve quality</strong>.<br><u>Contact us via our Discord server -&gt;</u> (<i>#open-ticked</i>) <u>if you want to contribute</u>.<br>Thank you, 3PA Studios.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> Be the captain of a Portuguese ship on a daring journey from Lisbon to Japan! </h2>Don't expect an easy ride, there are <strong>over 20 locations</strong>, <strong>50 tradable items</strong>, and <strong>multiple ships</strong> that <u>will not hesitate to steal them from you</u>.<br>Choose your <strong>play style</strong>... <strong>warriors, medics, cooks, entertainers, or sailors</strong>. <i>A mix of all?</i><br>Think carefully before making any decision, they will <strong>influence your future</strong> and also <strong>how the rest of the world sees you</strong>. <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Reputation <i> - Negotiators might not like a captain with a bad reputation... </i><br></li><li>Crew Morale <i> - Be careful with riots... </i><br></li><li>Crew Health <i> - You don't want your crew sick.. trust me. </i></li></ul>Along the way, there are multiple references to <strong>historical battles</strong> and items from Portuguese culture. Use your <strong>nautical journal</strong> to keep track of everything.<br><u> Are you the chosen one to reach Japan? </u><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2692450/extras/teste_titulo_steam.png?t=1709136030\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2692450/extras/battle_gif.gif?t=1709136030\" /><br><i>Pirates... they can cause some trouble but the reward could be worth it.</i><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2692450/extras/titulo_destination_steam.png?t=1709136030\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2692450/extras/locations_gif.gif?t=1709136030\" /><br><i>You are the Captain! Tell your crew where to go.</i><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2692450/extras/titulo_decision_steam.png?t=1709136030\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2692450/extras/events_gif.gif?t=1709136030\" /><br><i>Balancing every variable could be and will be challenging.</i><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2692450/extras/titulo_trade_steam.png?t=1709136030\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2692450/extras/trade_gif.gif?t=1709136030\" /><br><i>Some locations have certain resources and others don't... you can profit from that.</i><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2692450/extras/titulo_sea_conditions.png?t=1709136030\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2692450/extras/storm_gif.gif?t=1709136030\" /><br><i>Storms are a nightmare. Don't let your ship sink!</i>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"I got this!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2692450/24cc2397769d422afeff6f541e075842c6c5df25.jpg"},{"name":"So... you don't take debit card?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2692450/2d6d0df9548550463c5d39f9ba1055e8ca0aa3c8.jpg"},{"name":"Mr. Worldwide","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2692450/354e335269537422282132fc9879e